original_title: NPP wins in Colombo-Central, Moratuwa, Gampola, Nawalapitiya and Udunuwara
original_body_lines: The National People’s Power (NPP) has emerged victorious in the Moratuwa and Colombo-Central polling divisions in the Colombo District and Gampola, Nawalapitiya and Udunuwara polling divisions in Kandy District.
